OL,7,FMore than half a million vulnerable
OL,8,Fhouseholds with prepayment meters had
OL,9,Ftheir energy supply cut off in the past
OL,10,Fyear, i can reveal.
OL,12,FJanuary 2023 was a record month for the
OL,13,Fnumber of people who could not afford
OL,14,Fto top up their meters, with 5,086
OL,15,Findividuals asking Citizens Advice for
OL,16,Fhelp, figures from the charity show.
OL,18,FThis is more than the combined total
OL,19,Ffor January, February and March 2022,
OL,20,Fwhen 4,595 people asked for support.
